import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Form, InputNumber, Slider, Input, Select, Collapse } from 'antd'; const { Option } = Select; const { Panel } = Collapse; const ParameterSettings = ({ parameters, setParameters }) => { const handleChange = (key, value) => { setParameters({ ...parameters, [key]: value }); }; return (
handleChange('prompt', e.target.value)} rows={4} /> handleChange('max_tokens', value)} /> handleChange('temperature', value)} /> handleChange('top_p', value)} /> handleChange('min_p', value)} /> handleChange('top_k', value)} placeholder="-1 表示不限制" /> handleChange('presence_penalty', value)} /> handleChange('frequency_penalty', value)} /> handleChange('repetition_penalty', value)} />
); }; export default ParameterSettings;
